    "## Readings: Section 2.7\n",
    "\n",
    "### Section 2.7\n",
    "#### Transposes and Permutations\n",
    "\n",
    "##### Transposes\n",
    "\n",
    "Rules\n",
    "* Sum: $(A+B)^{T} = A^{T} + B^{T}$\n",
    "* Product: $(AB)^{T} = B^{T}A^{T}$ (note reversed order)\n",
    "* Inverse: $(A^{-1})^{T} = (A^{T})^{-1}$\n",
    "\n"
   ]
  }
